  "authors": [],
  "body": {
    "comment": "I simply do not believe this is a must-have during a year which needs austerity in spending.  This event in my mind will mostly be playing to a Cardano bubble and will not help with mass adoption which is the key area I would support spending marketing on. \n\nI'm using the lens of a career as an exec in one of the worlds largest advertising and event marketing firms, and through that lens I believe this will be unlikely to drive enough value during a period of austerity."
  },
  "hashAlgorithm": "blake2b-256"
}